        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Model form acceptance criteria",
        "description": "Bilinear isotropic hardening (BISO) material model for Ti-6Al-4V ELI; contact modeled with augmented Lagrange penalty; large-displacement formulation active. Model form assumptions documented and justified against published coupon data. Required: Gradation 3 (documented justification with sensitivity); achieved: Gradation 3."
      },
      "rationale": "The BISO plasticity model was selected based on published Ti-6Al-4V tensile coupon data and verified against independent dog-bone specimen simulations. Large-displacement effects were confirmed non-negligible above 10 mm displacement; the formulation is active throughout. Contact stiffness sensitivity was evaluated across a 10× range with <3% change in QoIs."
    },
    {
