        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "name": "Model inputs acceptance criteria",
        "description": "Material properties (E, σ_y, σ_u, n) sourced from ASTM F136 certificate of conformance and independent tensile coupons (N=5). Geometry from calibrated CMM measurements (±5 µm). Required: Gradation 3 (traceable, measured inputs with uncertainty); achieved: Gradation 3."
      },
      "rationale": "Young's modulus, yield strength, ultimate strength, and hardening exponent were measured from five Ti-6Al-4V ELI coupons machined from the same bar stock as the test constructs. Geometric inputs were derived from CMM measurements traceable to NIST length standards. Input uncertainty propagated via Latin Hypercube Sampling (N=200 runs)."
    },
    {
