      },
      "rationale": "Eleven constructs were assembled from a single production lot of non-cannulated 7.5 mm screws and UHMWPE blocks conforming to ASTM F1717. Device history records confirm lot traceability. Testing split across two laboratories provides inter-laboratory reproducibility evidence."
    },
    {
