      "rationale": "A parameter equivalency table was prepared prior to testing, mapping each experimental setup parameter to its FEA counterpart. Discrepancies in UHMWPE block modulus were resolved by measuring block stiffness from compression tests and updating FEA inputs accordingly. Equivalency confirmed by independent review."
