        "description": "E/uval metric computed for all three QoIs across all 11 constructs and both laboratories. Acceptance threshold: E/uval < 1.96 (95% confidence) AND percent difference < 10%. All QoIs pass both criteria. Required: Gradation 3; achieved: Gradation 4 (quantitative uncertainty-normalised comparison with documented statistical framework)."
