      "rationale": "The validation metric E/uval (model error normalised by combined experimental and simulation uncertainty) was computed for stiffness, yield force, and force at 40 mm displacement. All values fell below 1.96, confirming the model is within the acceptance threshold. Percent differences ranged from 1.2% to 7.8%, all below the 10% bound. Gradation 4 achieved due to the rigorous uncertainty-normalised comparison framework."
